{"id":847753145,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"7 months, 1 week","timestamp":1669080762,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"40 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/847753145/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Perfect Squares","memory":"43.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int numSquares(int n) {\n        int[] dp= new int[n+1];\n        dp[0]=1;\n        dp[1]=1;\n        for(int i=2;i<n+1;i++){\n            int ans=Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n            for(int j=1;j*j<=i;j++){\n                if(j*j==i){\n                    ans=0;\n                }\n                ans=Math.min(dp[i-j*j],ans);\n}\n            dp[i]=ans+1;\n        }\n        return dp[n];\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"perfect-squares","has_notes":false}
